{"tid":2441444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"好靚嘅畫面，遇上虛偽而殘暴嘅軍警","createTime":"2021-03-10T17:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T18:00:12.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd1cc907f16d3753a01bcbde6603065edaeecf8","tid":2441444,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/posts/1031774914017645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2Fposts%2F1031774914017645&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=950997b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/posts/1031774914017645</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkyp8PK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjkyp8PK.png&h=a5b3381e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Goodbye HK, Hello UK<br />\n<br />\n好靚嘅畫面，遇上虛偽而殘暴嘅軍警<br />\n<br />\n星期一早上，响緬甸城市Myitkyina一個教堂門外有示威活動，而軍警已經準備圍欄鎮壓。然後教堂嘅修女向啲軍警下跪，要求佢地唔好開槍，放過啲細路仔，要射就射死佢先。<br />\n<br />\n跟住好靚嘅畫面出現喇，就係啲軍警向跪拜，解釋自己只係執行職務制止示威。不過...响修女企起身擰轉面之後，就開始射催淚彈...然後聽到一下槍聲，有個示威者就倒地（被head shot），最後三人被殺。<br />\n<br />\n#緬甸軍方<br />\n<br />\n報導：<br />\n《Sky News》Nun tries to protect protesters as at least two killed in city of Myitkyina<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sky.com/story/youll-have-to-come-through-me-nun-tries-to-protect-myanmar-protesters-as-two-killed-12239838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fyoull-have-to-come-through-me-nun-tries-to-protect-myanmar-protesters-as-two-killed-12239838&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=0f1ecf46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sky.com/story/youll-have-to-come-through-me-nun-tries-to-protect-myanmar-protesters-as-two-killed-12239838</a><br />\n影片：<br />\nThree more protesters killed in Myanmar<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7fms1Tj3vdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7fms1Tj3vdk&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=7587c758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7fms1Tj3vdk</a>"},{"pid":"bb3a3bb8def89339d5ddeb0052f7d9a7b7b6b608","tid":2441444,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"即係殺左個修女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9028875ad699409792b25fcce6729219fe764d7a","tid":2441444,"uid":13000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"宣揚和平大愛 亦需要有相應武力係背後backup"},{"pid":"7d16b51962f5d148bcdb642dd7c7369c156d3e83","tid":2441444,"uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5148400425234434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fposts%2F5148400425234434&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=e309183f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5148400425234434</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：自由亞洲粵語 RFA Cantonese<br />\n <br />\n【緬甸修女下跪求警勿開槍】<br />\n【警稱只清路  後反口開槍致兩死】<br />\n<br />\n詳細報道 ➡️ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3rztC9d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3rztC9d&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=8abad17d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3rztC9d</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍警連日血腥鎮壓反對軍方政變的示威者，在北部城市密支那（Myitkyina），周一（8日）出現了修女向警察下跪的一幕。身穿白袍的45歲天主教修女努唐（Sister Ann Rose Nu Tawng）向警員下跪，求他們不要射殺示威者。兩名警員一同下跪，其中一人和她互相磕頭。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，有高級警員向她保證，說只是在清理道路，但不久軍警就向示威者開槍，至少2名示者頭部中彈死亡，3人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n有倡議團體表示，緬甸軍政府的血腥鎮壓，至今已造成超過60人死亡， 1800人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n而據《路透社》報道，部分緬甸警察拒絕執行命令向示威者開槍後，逃往印度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/779711395977191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fvideos%2F779711395977191&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=fed577f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/779711395977191</a>"},{"pid":"11584778d19b86e63e1f1fa26c74168194324785","tid":2441444,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb3a3bb8def89339d5ddeb0052f7d9a7b7b6b608","tid":2441444,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"即係殺左個修女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:10:07.000Z","msg":"應該冇，係打死咗修女後面幾個"},{"pid":"b230d820935dc387f5c48356e48b94472e6738f1","tid":2441444,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb3a3bb8def89339d5ddeb0052f7d9a7b7b6b608","tid":2441444,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"即係殺左個修女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"修女應該冇死到"},{"pid":"9e795af7b83aa5e5307e65b3ab40297f77e3f2bd","tid":2441444,"uid":209773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"警察呢個職業無論世界各地一講到政治就一定係賤種黎<br />\n係香港就講唔講政治都係賤種"},{"pid":"873a32acbcd5e6df06e0f4284d663ba8d6518fb1","tid":2441444,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"清理路障唔係清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8092ac25cc5b25bdbe5b4323d26fe6238d3bdc2","tid":2441444,"uid":20170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"有個post啲留言喺到笑鳩個修女<br />\n想問咁你想點<br />\n係呀個修女係大愛包容好撚膠<br />\n咁唔通你叫個修女勇武？"},{"pid":"9511297b099a15e5b2ca10119e6398a7bcf0e8c9","tid":2441444,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e795af7b83aa5e5307e65b3ab40297f77e3f2bd","tid":2441444,"uid":2097